item.title: MIXING | Reverb
item.dc:creator: Image Line Software
item.description: FL STUDIO MIXING | We asked you what tutorial to make next. You said Mixing! This time how reverberation or reverb is used create a sense of space and dimensionality in your track. In this tutorial we show you where to use reverb and some of the different reverb effects...
item.content:encoded:
FL STUDIO MIXING | We asked you what tutorial to make next. You said Mixing! This time how reverberation or reverb is used create a sense of space and dimensionality in your track. In this tutorial we show you where to use reverb and some of the different reverb effects available in FL Studio. 

Visit FL TUDIO @ YouTube

Reverb is the non-direct or reflected sound in a room or space. After the initial sound, reflections build up as they bounce around around the walls and off objects in the space. Every sound that isn’t going directly from the sound source to the listener’s ears is reverberation. In essence, reverb a set of closely spaced echoes, with usually first or early reflections that may be distinct and then a series of other echoes that blur together decaying in level. This wash of sound extends the length of short sounds and choruses longer ones.

Check the video information for links to the video index and project files.

item.title: MIXING | Delays
item.dc:creator: Image Line Software
item.description: FL STUDIO MIXING | We asked you what tutorial to make next. You said Mixing! Delays give your mix a sense of space and dimensionality without the density reverb can create. In this tutorial we show you where to use delay and some of the delay effects available in FL...
item.content:encoded:
FL STUDIO MIXING | We asked you what tutorial to make next. You said Mixing! Delays give your mix a sense of space and dimensionality without the density reverb can create. In this tutorial we show you where to use delay and some of the delay effects available in FL Studio. 

Visit FL TUDIO @ YouTube

Delays are often perceived as echo and can make the listener feel like sounds exist in a room or space while avoiding adding the wash of sound a reverb creates. This can help open up the mix. Think of delay as a Reverb lite! They are also perfect for special effects like stereo ping-pongs and more. 

Check the video information for links to the video index and project files.

item.content:encoded:
FL STUDIO MIXING | We asked you what tutorial to make next. You said Mixing! Today, the Stereo Imaging or how to mix the Stereo Field. What is it and how to make the best use of it to improve your mixes?

Visit FL TUDIO @ YouTube

The Stereo Image of a mix defines the spatial location of all the sounds in it. You can mix with the stereo field in mind to separate sounds spatially, to better improve their definition, recognition or to create a sense of spatial realism. This tutorial shows you what tools you already have in FL Studio to achieve a great Stereo Image.

Check the video information for links to the video index and project files.

item.title: FL STUDIO MOBILE | 3.6 Update
item.dc:creator: Image Line Software
item.description: FL Studio Mobile: 3.2.19 is now available for Android, iOS and Windows. Now with time signatures.
item.content:encoded:
FL STUDIO MOBILE | We are pleased to release FL Studio Mobile 3.6. Introducing a new Stereo FX plugin (Spacer), upgraded Compressor UI with visualizations, File browser improvements with long-tap send to Playlist functions and more. Another Free Update for FL Studio Mobile Users.

Read the manual or watch all the FL Studio Mobile tutorial videos here.

 

What's New?

  • Spacer (FX module) - Stereo image enhancer.
  • Compressor - Improved interface with visualizations.
  • Improved audio device support - Multi-input selection. Multi-track recording. Output device selection (Windows).
  • File browser improvements - Long press actions, 'Copy' for files & folders, 'Create channels' for creating multiple Channels. Last scroll position remembered.
  • Android 11 Scoped Storage - Google mandated API change moves your Mobile App Data to a protected folder. NOTE: Deleting FL Studio Mobile will delete your project data! Make sure to backup your data from the FILES tab.
  • Bugfixes and stability improvements

No matter where you are or what hardware platform you choose, FL Studio Mobile is there ready to support your best creative moments.

Image-Line

item.content:encoded:
We have teamed up with Alan Walker ⚡ and Imanbek ⚡ to bring you the official Sweet Dreams Remix Contest! Join for a chance to have your song released as an official remix + other amazing prizes. Check the link below for more info and to download the stems for your remix!

Click here to get started

  

 Alan Walker, Imanbek & FL Studio Celebrating Bedroom Producers Everywhere

What's happening?

To celebrate the release of Alan's latest single “Sweet Dreams” we have teamed up with Alan and Imanbek to bring you the official Sweet Dreams remix contest. We have some amazing prizes lined up for you and the winning track will be released as an official remix! All you have to do is to download the stems, make your own remix and submit it on this website before July 23rd. The winners will be announced on July 30. Start here.

Bedroom producers!

The FL Studio team is proud to have played its part in the home music revolution. Many of today's top music artists, including Alan Walker and Imanbek launched their music careers with FL Studio from a bedroom studio. Why not start your own journey too? You can download FL Studio and use the trial for an unlimited time. Export audio and video.

TRY FL Studio here OR  BUY FL Studio here

The All-purpose envelope works with multiple menu entries and is a powerful sound design tool. Even experienced Edison users are...
item.content:encoded:
FL STUDIO EDISON | In the final video of our 6 part series we cover the Editor Envelopes. While the Pan, Volume and Stereo Separation envelopes are almost self explanatory. The All-purpose envelope works with multiple menu entries and is a powerful sound design tool. Even experienced Edison users are likely to learn a thing or two ...

Visit FL TUDIO @ YouTube

Edison is a fully integrated audio editing and recording tool. Edison loads into an effect slot (in any mixer track) and will then record or play audio from that position. You may load as many instances of Edison as you require in any number of Mixer Tracks or Effects slots. It is included with all editions of FL Studio from Producer Edition and up. Image-Line
